dc_description_s: This data represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Grant County, Wisconsin in 2019. [This data is built from referencing the tie sheets that have been recorded in the Land Information Office specifically for this remonumentation project. The project was started in the early 1990s but, due to a lack of attribute and/or metadata in any existing GIS formats. the project has undergone structural changed. Remonumentation (re)started in 2017 and has all work being performed by a single source to maintain data/procedural integrity.]
